history.content: How would a schedule like this be for next semester? Of these three techs I know EE 126 will definitely be my hardest one, but I'm feeling pretty okay about CS 161 and EE 128. I've taken on similar workloads in the past, but I'm worried about how much extra work I might have to put into a class like EE 126, and whether that might be "too much"
history.subject: CS 161 + EE 126 + EE 128 + Humanities
